1990年3月11日，{{le|立陶宛最高委員會|Supreme Council – Reconstituent Seimas}}簽署[[立陶宛復國法案|立陶宛復國法案]]宣布立陶宛恢復独立，為第一個自蘇聯宣布獨立的共和國，4月22日蘇聯宣布對立陶宛{{le|蘇聯對立陶宛的經濟封鎖|Soviet economic blockade of Lithuania|實行經濟封鎖}}，停止向立陶宛供應石油等原物料<ref>{{cite web |author1=Martha Brill Olcott |title=The Lithuanian Crisis |url=https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/russian-federation/1990-06-01/lithuanian-crisis |website=www.foreignaffairs.com |access-date=2018-11-18 |date=1990 |quote=For over two years Lithuania has been moving toward reclaiming its independence. This drive reached a crescendo on 11 March 1990, when the Supreme Soviet of Lithuania declared the republic no longer bound by Soviet law. The act reasserted the independence Lithuania had declared more than seventy years before, a declaration unilaterally annulled by the U.S.S.R. in 1940 when it annexed Lithuania as the result of a pact between Stalin and Hitler. |archive-date=2021-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623222200/https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/russian-federation/1990-06-01/lithuanian-crisis |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隔年1月蘇聯試圖策劃兵變推翻新獨立的立陶宛政府，莫斯科當局認為立陶宛經濟情況不佳，當地人應會強烈支持政變<ref>{{cite web|title=10 svarbiausių 1991–ųjų sausio įvykių, kuriuos privalote žinoti|url=https://www.15min.lt/naujiena/aktualu/lietuva/10-svarbiausiu-1991-uju-sausio-ivykiu-kuriuos-privalote-zinoti-56-565845|website=15min.lt|access-date=2016-01-13|archive-date=2021-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625115355/https://www.15min.lt/naujiena/aktualu/lietuva/10-svarbiausiu-1991-uju-sausio-ivykiu-kuriuos-privalote-zinoti-56-565845|dead-url=no}}</ref>，便派遣軍隊進攻維爾紐斯政府大樓，是為[[立陶宛一月事件|立陶宛一月事件]]，但立陶宛人多支持獨立的政府，故政變未能成功，蘇聯在國際壓力下被迫撤軍<ref name="bbc">{{cite news|title=On This Day 13 January 1991: Bloodshed at Lithuanian TV station|work=BBC News|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/onthisday/hi/dates/stories/january/13/newsid_4059000/4059959.stm|access-date=2011-09-13|date=1991-01-13|archive-date=2017-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109010731/http://news.bbc.co.uk/onthisday/hi/dates/stories/january/13/newsid_4059000/4059959.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title=Soviet crackdown; Soviet loyalists in charge after attack in Lithuania; 13 dead; curfew is imposed| author=Bill Keller| newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]| date=1991-01-14| access-date=2009-12-18| url=https://www.nytimes.com/1991/01/14/world/soviet-crackdown-soviet-loyalists-charge-after-attack-lithuania-13-dead-curfew.html?pagewanted=all| archive-date=2021-04-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417195108/https://www.nytimes.com/1991/01/14/world/soviet-crackdown-soviet-loyalists-charge-after-attack-lithuania-13-dead-curfew.html?pagewanted=all| dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月31日蘇軍在立陶宛與白俄羅斯的邊境攻擊立陶宛邊檢人員，造成7人死亡（[[蘇聯特別用途機動單位襲擊立陶宛邊境檢察站事件|梅迪尼恩凱大屠殺]]）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://coldwarsites.net/country/lithuania/memorial-medininkai|title=Memorial. Medininkai – Cold war sites|website=coldwarsites.net|access-date=2021-06-26|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511215634/https://coldwarsites.net/country/lithuania/memorial-medininkai/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1991年2月11日[[冰島議會|冰島議會]]決議指冰島政府1922年對立陶宛獨立的承認仍有效，且從未正式承認蘇聯佔有立陶宛<ref>{{cite news |title=Svo fljótt sem verða má |url=http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?pageId=2927190 |access-date=2018-10-28 |work=[[Þjóðviljinn|Þjóðviljinn]] |date=1991-02-12 |language=is |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413074631/http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?pageId=2927190 |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，兩國應盡快恢復外交關係<ref>{{cite news |title=Stjórnmálasamband verði tekið upp svo fljótt sem verða má |url=http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?pageId=1738122 |access-date=2018-10-28 |work=[[Morgunblaðið|Morgunblaðið]] |date=1991-02-12 |language=is |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413074310/http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?pageId=1738122 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Viðurkenning á sjálfstæði í fullu gildi |url=http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?pageId=2581110 |access-date=2018-10-28 |work=[[Dagblaðið_Vísir|Dagblaðið Vísir]] |date=1991-02-12 |language=is |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413074432/http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?pageId=2581110 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1991年9月6日苏联才承认其独立。9月17日立陶宛加入[[聯合國|聯合國]]。1992年10月25日立陶宛公投制定現行憲法，1993年2月14日全民直選選出[[阿尔吉尔达斯·布拉藻斯卡斯|阿尔吉尔达斯·布拉藻斯卡斯]]為首任[[立陶宛總統|立陶宛總統]]，同年8月31日[[俄羅斯聯邦軍隊|俄羅斯軍隊]]全數撤離立陶宛<ref>{{cite book| author=Richard J. Krickus| chapter=Democratization in Lithuania| editor=K. Dawisha and B. Parrott| title=The Consolidation of Democracy in East-Central Europe| date=June 1997| page=[https://archive.org/details/consolidationofd0000unse/page/344 344]| chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NRkpNovMd_cC&lpg=PA344| isbn=978-0-521-59938-2| url=https://archive.org/details/consolidationofd0000unse/page/344}}</ref>；2001年5月31日立陶宛加入[[世界貿易組織|世界貿易組織]]<ref>{{cite web |title=WTO - Accessions: Lithuania |url=https://www.wto.org/english/thewto_e/acc_e/a1_lituanie_e.htm |website=www.wto.org |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2021-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531070148/https://www.wto.org/english/thewto_e/acc_e/a1_lituanie_e.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2004年3月29日加入[[北大西洋公約組織|北大西洋公約組織]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Lithuania's membership in the North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) |url=https://www.urm.lt/default/en/foreign-policy/lithuania-in-the-region-and-the-world/lithuanias-security-policy/lithuanian-membership-in-nato |website=urm.lt |access-date=2021-03-30 |date=2014-02-05 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417181725/https://www.urm.lt/default/en/foreign-policy/lithuania-in-the-region-and-the-world/lithuanias-security-policy/lithuanian-membership-in-nato |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同年5月1日正式加入[[欧盟|欧盟]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Membership |url=https://www.urm.lt/default/en/foreign-policy/lithuania-in-the-region-and-the-world/lithuania-member-of-the-european-union/membership |website=urm.lt |access-date=2021-03-30 |date=2016-01-06 |archive-date=2021-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210626050010/https://www.urm.lt/default/en/foreign-policy/lithuania-in-the-region-and-the-world/lithuania-member-of-the-european-union/membership |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2007年12月21日加入[[申根公約|申根公約]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Lithuania has joined the Schengen Area |url=http://no.mfa.lt/no/en/news/lithuania-has-joined-the-schengen-area |website=mfa.lt |access-date=2021-03-30 |date=2008-01-16 |archive-date=2021-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210626050010/http://no.mfa.lt/no/en/news/lithuania-has-joined-the-schengen-area |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2015年1月1日加入[[歐元區|歐元區]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kropaite |first1=Zivile |title=Lithuania joins Baltic neighbours in euro club |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30635826 |website=BBC News |access-date=2021-03-30 |date=2015-01-01 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418104637/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30635826 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2018年7月4日加入[[經濟合作暨發展組織|經濟合作暨發展組織]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Lithuania officially becomes the 36th OECD member |url=https://lrv.lt/en/news/lithuania-officially-becomes-the-36th-oecd-member |website=lrv.lt |access-date=2021-03-30 |date=2018-07-05 |archive-date=2021-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623223003/https://lrv.lt/en/news/lithuania-officially-becomes-the-36th-oecd-member |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

