== 经济與產業 ==
{{main|立陶宛經濟}}
[[File:Lithuania's_GDP_per_capita_compared_to_rest_of_the_world_(2020).png|thumb]]
立陶宛的貨幣原為[[立陶宛立特|立陶宛立特]]（LTL），2015年1月1日起加入[[歐元區|歐元區]]，正式改用歐元為國內流通貨幣，3.4528立陶宛立特可兌換1歐元<ref name=iso4217news2014>{{cite web | url=http://www.currency-iso.org/dam/downloads/dl_currency_iso_amendment_159.docx | title=ISO Currency – ISO 4217 Amendment Number 159 | publisher=SIX Interbank Clearing | work=Currency Code Services – ISO 4217 Maintenance Agency | date=2014-08-15 | access-date=2021-07-01 | archive-date=2021-04-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430211020/https://www.currency-iso.org/dam/downloads/dl_currency_iso_amendment_159.docx | dead-url=no }}</ref>。立陶宛為[[世界銀行|世界銀行]]定義的[[高收入經濟體|高收入經濟體]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://datahelpdesk.worldbank.org/knowledgebase/articles/906519|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111190936/https://datahelpdesk.worldbank.org/knowledgebase/articles/906519|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-11|title=World Bank Country and Lending Groups – World Bank Data Help Desk|date=2018-01-11|website=Datahelpdesk.worldbank.org|access-date=2021-07-01}}</ref>。據2016年的數據，其國內服務業佔GDP比重為68.3%、工業佔28.5%、農業則佔3.3%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/lithuania/|title=GDP – composition, by sector of origin|access-date=2018-03-19|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703005652/https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/lithuania/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年立陶宛的出口物品中，農產品與食物佔比18.3%，化學製品與塑膠佔17.8%，機器與器具佔15.8%，礦產佔14.7%，木材與家具佔12.5%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.enterpriselithuania.com/en/lithuanian-export-map/2017-2/|title=Lithuanian export map|website=Enterpriselithuania.com|access-date=2018-04-07|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703112426/https://www.enterpriselithuania.com/en/lithuanian-export-map/2017-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年立陶宛的最大出口國為俄羅斯，佔比14%，其次依序為拉脫維亞（9.9%）、波蘭（9.1%）、德國（7.7%）、愛沙尼亞（5.3%）、瑞典（4.8%）與英國（4.3%）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://atlas.media.mit.edu/en/visualize/tree_map/hs92/export/ltu/show/all/2016/|title=Where does Lithuania export to? (2016)|access-date=2018-03-19|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024223637/http://atlas.media.mit.edu/en/visualize/tree_map/hs92/export/ltu/show/all/2016/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[File:GNI-2016-Lithuania.png|thumb]]（GNI）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GNP.PCAP.PP.CD?end=2016&locations=LT-EU&start=2016&type=shaded&view=map&year=2016|title=Lithuania 2016, GNI per capita, PPP (current international $)|website=Data.worldbank.org|access-date=2018-03-18|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703110721/https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GNP.PCAP.PP.CD?end=2016&locations=LT-EU&start=2016&type=shaded&view=map&year=2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>]]
立陶宛因2000年至2009年經濟快速成長，被譽為[[波羅的之虎|波羅的之虎]]，2007年的經濟成長率高達11.1%，但隨後受[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|環球金融危機]]影響而出現嚴重衰退，2009年GDP重挫14.9%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.seb.lt/sites/default/files/web/document/lietuvos_ekonomikos_apzvalga_LMR/lmr58_0.pdf |title=Lithuanian Macroeconomic Review No 58 |publisher=SEB |date=December 2014 |access-date=2015-05-22 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308134859/https://www.seb.lt/sites/default/files/web/document/lietuvos_ekonomikos_apzvalga_LMR/lmr58_0.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2010年[[失業率|失業率]]升至17.8%<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.seb.lt/documents/660/662 | title="Lietuvos makroekonomikos apžvalga" nr. 62 | publisher=SEB | date=April 2014 | access-date=2016-09-07 | archive-date=2021-07-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703115931/https://www.seb.lt/documents/660/662 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後經濟成長緩慢回升，但成長幅度不如2009年前的強勢，但[[國際貨幣基金|國際貨幣基金]]認為立陶宛的財政狀況然堪稱穩健，2016年的[[赤字率|赤字率]]從前一年的42.7%降為40%（金融危機以前的2008年赤字率僅為15%）<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.imf.org/~/media/Files/Publications/CR/2017/cr17177.ashx | title=REPUBLIC OF LITHUANIA. 2017 ARTICLE IV CONSULTATION—PRESS RELEASE AND STAFF REPORT | publisher=IMF | format=PDF | page=4 | access-date=2018-03-28 | archive-date=2021-03-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312130212/https://www.imf.org/~/media/Files/Publications/CR/2017/cr17177.ashx | dead-url=no }}</ref>。立陶宛平均有超過95%的[[外商直接投資|外商直接投資]]（FDI）來自其他歐盟國家，其中以[[瑞典|瑞典]]為最高，佔約20%至30%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lb.lt/lt/tiesiogines-uzsienio-investicijos-lietuvoje-pagal-sali-1|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109194528/https://www.lb.lt/lt/tiesiogines-uzsienio-investicijos-lietuvoje-pagal-sali-1|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-09|title=Tiesioginės užsienio investicijos Lietuvoje pagal šalį – Lietuvos bankas|date=2018-01-09|access-date=2021-07-01}}</ref>，2017年立陶宛的FDI達到高峰。

2004年至2016年立陶宛有大量人口出走，約兩成人口移民至其他國家，原因包括收入不足、尋找新的職缺或求學等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.delfi.lt/news/daily/lithuania/ieskodami-darbuotoju-jau-verciasi-per-galva-net-tokiomis-algomis-nepavyksta-sugundyti.d?id=77973215|title=Ieškodami darbuotojų jau verčiasi per galvą: net tokiomis algomis nepavyksta sugundyti|language=lt|website=delfi.lt|access-date=2018-05-13|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703110800/https://www.delfi.lt/news/daily/lithuania/ieskodami-darbuotoju-jau-verciasi-per-galva-net-tokiomis-algomis-nepavyksta-sugundyti.d?id=77973215|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成國內勞動人力的缺乏與薪資的上漲<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.delfi.lt/verslas/verslas/emigracija-smogia-negailestingai-lietuvoje-vis-labiau-truksta-darbuotoju.d?id=75467805|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111194908/https://www.delfi.lt/verslas/verslas/emigracija-smogia-negailestingai-lietuvoje-vis-labiau-truksta-darbuotoju.d?id=75467805|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-11|title=Emigracija smogia negailestingai: Lietuvoje vis labiau trūksta darbuotojų – DELFI Verslas|date=2018-01-11|access-date=2021-07-01}}</ref><ref name="archive org 11">{{cite web|url=https://verslas.lrytas.lt/izvalgos-ir-nuomones/2017/06/13/news/ekspertai-ispeja-virs-lietuvos-ekonomikos-kaupiasi-debesys-1665764/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111195018/https://verslas.lrytas.lt/izvalgos-ir-nuomones/2017/06/13/news/ekspertai-ispeja-virs-lietuvos-ekonomikos-kaupiasi-debesys-1665764/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-11|title=Ekonomistai įspėja: virš Lietuvos kaupiasi debesys|date=2018-01-11|access-date=2021-07-01}}</ref>。

[[File:Exports-2016-Lithuania.png|thumb]]
2019年，立陶宛成人的平均資產為50,524美元，國家資產總值估計為1150億美元<ref>{{cite book |url=https://www.credit-suisse.com/media/assets/corporate/docs/about-us/research/publications/global-wealth-databook-2019.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023104250/https://www.credit-suisse.com/media/assets/corporate/docs/about-us/research/publications/global-wealth-databook-2019.pdf |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2019-10-23 |title=Global Wealth Report 2019 |publisher=Credit Suisse |year=2019 |access-date=2021-07-01 }}</ref> 。2020年全國平均月薪為1000歐元<ref name="https://osp.stat.gov.lt">{{Cite web|url=https://osp.stat.gov.lt/informaciniai-pranesimai?eventId=242633|title=Darbo užmokestis šalyje|website=osp.stat.gov.lt|access-date=2021-07-01|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703110844/https://osp.stat.gov.lt/informaciniai-pranesimai?eventId=242633|dead-url=no}}</ref>（[[購買力平價|購買力平價]]為2200歐元<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://data.oecd.org/earnwage/average-wages.htm|title=Earnings and wages – Average wages – OECD Data|website=theOECD|access-date=2021-07-01|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703110858/https://data.oecd.org/earnwage/average-wages.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>）。該國的[[生活成本|生活成本]]相對較低，2016年的{{le|家庭消費支出|Household final consumption expenditure}}（HFCE）為63，低於歐盟平均的102<ref>{{cite web|title=Comparative price levels of consumer goods and services – Statistics Explained|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Comparative_price_levels_of_consumer_goods_and_services|website=[[Eurostat|Eurostat]]|access-date=2018-01-16|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501013831/https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Comparative_price_levels_of_consumer_goods_and_services|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

立陶宛稅制為[[單一稅|單一稅]]，據[[歐洲統計局|歐洲統計局]]統計，立陶宛的個人稅率（15%）與公司稅率（15%）在歐盟國家中都算是相當低的<ref name="epp.eurostat.ec.europa.eu">{{cite web | url=http://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/resources/documents/taxation/gen_info/economic_analysis/tax_structures/2014/report.pdf | title=Taxation trends in the European Union | publisher=Eurostat | date=2014 | access-date=2015-05-22 | dead-url=yes | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509130331/http://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/resources/documents/taxation/gen_info/economic_analysis/tax_structures/2014/report.pdf | archive-date=2015-05-09 }}</ref>，其隱性稅率為9.8%，是歐盟國家中最低的。立陶宛國內有7個[[自由港|自由貿易區]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Pramoniniai parkai ir LEZ|url=https://ukmin.lrv.lt/lt/veiklos-sritys/investiciju-veiklos-sritis/pramoniniai-parkai-ir-lez|website=ukmin.lrv.lt|access-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424071555/https://ukmin.lrv.lt/lt/veiklos-sritys/investiciju-veiklos-sritis/pramoniniai-parkai-ir-lez|archive-date=2018-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

近年立陶宛的[[資訊科技|資訊科技]]快速發展，2016年產值已有19億歐元<ref>{{cite book|last1=Samuolis|first1=Gediminas|title=Informacinės technologijos Lietuvoje|date=2017|publisher=Lietuvos statistikos departamentas|location=Vilnius|page=8|url=https://ivpk.lrv.lt/uploads/ivpk/documents/files/Naujienos/IT%20Lietuvoje%202017.pdf|access-date=2021-07-01|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308150136/https://ivpk.lrv.lt/uploads/ivpk/documents/files/Naujienos/IT%20Lietuvoje%202017.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年歐洲的第一個國際區塊鏈中心在立陶宛首都維爾紐斯成立<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kostaki |first1=Irene |title=Lithuania debuts as EU gateway for global blockchain industry |url=https://www.neweurope.eu/article/lithuania-debuts-eu-gateway-global-blockchain-industry/ |website=Neweurope.eu |date=2018-01-31 |quote=The Lithuanian capital Vilnius launched Europe’s first international Blockchain Centre on January 27, making it the EU’s only hub for the digital ledger. The new hub will help Europe connect with partner Blockchain Centres in Australia, China, Canada, the UK, Belgium, Denmark, Georgia, Gibraltar, Ukraine, Israel, and Latvia. |access-date=2018-07-14 |archive-date=2021-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703110944/https://www.neweurope.eu/article/lithuania-debuts-eu-gateway-global-blockchain-industry/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

