立陶宛总人口不足300万，人口老龄化程度日趋严重，且正面臨[[少子化|少子化]]，2014年統計顯示全國人口中14歲以下者佔13.5%，15至64歲者為69.5%，65歲以上則為16.8%<ref name="CIA">{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/lithuania/|publisher=CIA World Factbook|title=Lithuania|access-date=2021-07-01|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703005652/https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/lithuania/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[總和生育率|總和生育率]]約為1.59<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2127rank.html |title=Country Comparison: Total Fertility Rate |work=CIA World Factbook |access-date=2021-07-12 |archive-date=2009-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028133713/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2127rank.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，29%的新生兒為未婚婦女所生<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/tgm/table.do?tab=table&plugin=1&language=en&pcode=tps00018 |title=Eurostat – Tables, Graphs and Maps Interface (TGM) table |website=Ec.europa.eu |date=2015-09-28 |access-date=2016-09-07 |archive-date=2016-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527142604/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/tgm/table.do?tab=table&plugin=1&language=en&pcode=tps00018 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[初婚年齡|初婚年齡]]女性為27歲、男性則為29.3歲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://w3.unece.org/PXWeb2015/pxweb/en/STAT/STAT__30-GE__02-Families_households/052_en_GEFHAge1stMarige_r.px/table/tableViewLayout1/?rxid=47a01215-08b5-4ba5-ade3-d9a4455878d4 |title=Select variable and values – UNECE Statistical Database |website=W3.unece.org |date=2016-02-09 |access-date=2016-04-30}}</ref>。

同时，立陶宛人口外流现象非常严重。1992年立陶宛人口达到370万的峰值，随后逐年递减，到2017年已减至285万<ref>{{cite news |author1=郭明芳 |title=立陶宛议会批准应对人口问题的战略 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-09/21/c_1123464484.htm#:~:text=%EF%BC%91%EF%BC%99%EF%BC%99%EF%BC%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%AB%8B%E9%99%B6%E5%AE%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0,%E5%B0%86%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B3%EF%BC%92%EF%BC%94%EF%BC%90%E4%B8%87%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D |accessdate=2021-05-25 |agency=新华社 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128163222/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-09/21/c_1123464484.htm#:~:text=%EF%BC%91%EF%BC%99%EF%BC%99%EF%BC%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%AB%8B%E9%99%B6%E5%AE%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0,%E5%B0%86%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B3%EF%BC%92%EF%BC%94%EF%BC%90%E4%B8%87%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
