立陶宛的族群自新石器時代起即沒有太大的變動，沒有大規模的人口取代，因此現今[[立陶宛人|立陶宛人]]的遺傳組成可能與古代的立陶宛人相差不遠<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Česnys | first1 = G. | year = 1991 | title = Anthropological roots of the Lithuanians | journal = Science, Arts and Lithuania | volume = 1 | pages = 4–10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media |people=akad. Rimantas Jankauskas |date=2018-05-06|title="Mokslo ekspresas": tūkstantmečiai kapai atskleidžia Lietuvos priešistorės paslaptis|medium=Video |language=lt |url=https://www.delfi.lt/video/laidos/mokslo-ekspresas/mokslo-ekspresas-tukstantmeciai-kapai-atskleidzia-lietuvos-priesistores-paslaptis.d?id=77886901 |access-date=2018-05-11 |time=04:06}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=The genetic prehistory of the Baltic Sea region |authors=Alissa Mittnik, Chuan-Chao Wang, Saskia Pfrengle, Mantas Daubaras, Gunita Zariņa, Fredrik Hallgren, Raili Allmäe, Valery Khartanovich, Vyacheslav Moiseyev, Mari Tõrv, Anja Furtwängler, Aida Andrades Valtueña, Michal Feldman, Christos Economou, Markku Oinonen, Andrejs Vasks, Elena Balanovska, David Reich, Rimantas Jankauskas, Wolfgang Haak, Stephan Schiffels & Johannes Krause |journal=Nature Communications|volume=9 |doi=10.1038/s41467-018-02825-9|pmid=29382937 |pmc=5789860 |issue=1|pages=442 |bibcode=2018NatCo...9..442M|year=2018}}</ref>，且立陶宛人在遺傳上的同質性很高，沒有明顯的子群<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://images.katalogas.lt/maleidykla/act41/A-01.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080227130058/http://images.katalogas.lt/maleidykla/act41/A-01.pdf |archive-date=2008-02-27 |title=Mitochondrial DNA Sequence Analysis in the Lithuanian Population |author=Dalia Kasperavičiūtė and Vaidutis Kučinskas |journal=Acta Medica Lituanica |year=2004 |volume=11 |issue=1 |pages=1–6 |dead-url=yes |access-date=2021-07-12 }}</ref>。2004年的一項[[粒線體DNA|粒線體DNA]]分析顯示立陶宛人與[[斯拉夫民族|斯拉夫民族]]與[[芬兰-乌戈尔语族|芬兰-乌-{戈}-尔语族人]]較為接近，[[人类Y染色体DNA单倍型类群|Y染色體單倍群]]分析則顯示立陶宛人與[[愛沙尼亞人|愛沙尼亞人]]和[[拉脫維亞人|拉脫維亞人]]最為接近<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=15469421 |author=D Kasperaviciūte, V Kucinskas and M Stoneking |url=http://www.eva.mpg.de/genetics/pdf/Kasperavicuite.2004.pdf |title=Y Chromosome and Mitochondrial DNA Variation in Lithuanians |year=2004 |volume=68 |issue=Pt 5 |pages=438–52 |doi=10.1046/j.1529-8817.2003.00119.x |journal=Annals of Human Genetics |s2cid=26562505 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225205400/http://www.eva.mpg.de/genetics/pdf/Kasperavicuite.2004.pdf |archive-date=2009-02-25 |access-date=2021-07-12 }}</ref>。

立陶宛約有六分之五的人口為立陶宛人，為波羅的海三國中族群同質性最高的國家，2015年統計顯示全國2,921,262人中有84.2%為以[[立陶宛語|立陶宛語]]為母語的立陶宛人，其他則為[[波蘭人|波蘭人]]（6.6%）、[[俄羅斯人|俄羅斯人]]（5.8%）、[[白俄羅斯人|白俄羅斯人]]（1.2%）與[[烏克蘭人|烏克蘭人]]（0.5%）等{{le|立陶宛的少數族裔|Ethnic minorities in Lithuania|少數族裔}}<ref name="2011abar"/>，[[波蘭裔立陶宛人|波蘭裔立陶宛人]]是境內人數最多的少數族裔，多居住於立陶宛東南部（維爾紐斯地區）；{{le|俄羅斯裔立陶宛人|Russians in Lithuania|俄羅斯裔}}次之，多集中在維爾紐斯和克莱佩达兩市，分別佔當地人口的12%<ref>Delfi (2012) [http://www.delfi.lt/news/daily/lithuania/kas-penktas-klaipedietis-yra-rusas-vilnietis-kas-astuntas.d?id=59643343 Kas penktas klaipėdietis yra rusas, vilnietis – kas aštuntas] {{Wayback|url=http://www.delfi.lt/news/daily/lithuania/kas-penktas-klaipedietis-yra-rusas-vilnietis-kas-astuntas.d?id=59643343 |date=20160611212439 }}; Retrieved on 7 January 2017</ref>與19.6%<ref name="osp.stat.gov.lt">{{cite web|url=https://osp.stat.gov.lt/documents/10180/217110/Gyv_kalba_tikyba.pdf/1d9dac9a-3d45-4798-93f5-941fed00503f|format=PDF|title=GYVENTOJAI PAGAL TAUTYBĘ, GIMTĄJĄ KALBĄ IR TIKYBĄ : Lietuvos Respublikos 2011 metų visuotinio gyventojų ir būstų surašymo rezultatai|website=Ops.stat.gov.lt|access-date=2018-10-18|archive-date=2020-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313110843/https://osp.stat.gov.lt/documents/10180/217110/Gyv_kalba_tikyba.pdf/1d9dac9a-3d45-4798-93f5-941fed00503f|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在東部城鎮[[維薩吉納斯|維薩吉納斯]]佔過半數人口（52%）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.visaginas.lt/town/inhabit?lang=en |title=The inhabitants |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071219181605/http://www.visaginas.lt/town/inhabit?lang=en |archive-date=2007-12-19 |dead-url=yes |access-date=2021-07-13 }}</ref>；立陶宛還有約3,000名[[羅姆人|羅姆人]]，多住在維爾紐斯、考那斯和帕內韋日斯<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tspmi.vu.lt/files/mprojektai/finallithsecpapergalutinis.pdf |title=Lithuanian Security and Foreign Policy |website=Tspmi.vu.lt |access-date=2011-06-05 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325051515/http://www.tspmi.vu.lt/files/mprojektai/finallithsecpapergalutinis.pdf |archive-date=2009-03-25 }}</ref>；且有約3,000名[[利普卡韃靼人|利普卡韃靼人]]（立陶宛韃靼人），其祖先約於14世紀末開始自[[金帳汗國|金帳汗國]]等地遷至立陶宛大公國<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eki.ee/books/redbook/lithuanian_tatars.shtml|title=The Red Book of the Peoples of the Russian Empire|website=Eki.ee|access-date=2021-07-13|archive-date=2017-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608180539/http://www.eki.ee/books/redbook/lithuanian_tatars.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外立陶宛原本有許多[[立陶宛猶太人|猶太人]]，自18世紀起即為歐洲重要的{{tsl|en|History of the Jews in Lithuania|立陶宛猶太人歷史|猶太社群}}，1941年6月（納粹入侵前）約有22萬名猶太人，幾乎都在[[立陶宛猶太人大屠殺|大屠殺]]中遇害<ref name="Bubnys_vanished219">{{cite book |author=Arūnas Bubnys |chapter=Holocaust in Lithuania: An Outline of the Major Stages and Their Results |title=The Vanished World of Lithuanian Jews |publisher=Rodopi |year=2004 |isbn=978-90-420-0850-2 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mdXRKbcyi5oC&pg=PA219 |pages=218–219 |access-date=2021-07-14 |archive-date=2021-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623222136/https://books.google.com/books?id=mdXRKbcyi5oC&pg=PA219 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia|title=Lithuania|url=http://www.ushmm.org/wlc/en/article.php?ModuleId=10005444|encyclopedia=Holocaust Encyclopedia|publisher=United States Holocaust Memorial Museum|access-date=2012-04-12|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BhO4sxW4?url=http://www.ushmm.org/wlc/en/article.php?ModuleId=10005444|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2009年統計顯示立陶宛的猶太人僅有4,000人<ref name="Stats">{{cite web |title=Population at the beginning of the year by ethnicity |url=http://www.stat.gov.lt/en/pages/view/?id=1731&PHPSESSID=a2cc98ebfc3a13b8297889cb6f68d571 |work=Statistics Lithuania |access-date=2012-04-12 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070604090852/http://www.stat.gov.lt/en/pages/view/?id=1731&PHPSESSID=311ec85274c89154e6f4befbc159a0e8 |archive-date=2007-06-04 }}</ref>。

立陶宛的官方語言為立陶宛語，部分地區也有相當的[[波蘭語|波蘭語]]、[[俄語|俄語]]、[[白俄羅斯語|白俄羅斯語]]和[[烏克蘭語|烏克蘭語]]人口，其中以[[沙爾奇寧凱區|沙爾奇寧凱區]]（80%人口為波蘭裔）、[[維爾紐斯區|維爾紐斯區]]和[[維薩吉納斯_(市鎮)|維薩吉納斯]]最多，有極少數尚存的猶太人仍使用[[意第緒語|意第緒語]]。立陶宛法律將少數族裔的語言列入學校教育中，在少數族裔集中的地區設有許多公立學校教授這些語言<ref>{{cite web|url=https://lrkm.lrv.lt/en/activities/national-minorities|title=Ministry of Culture of the Republic of Lithuania, National Minorities|access-date=2020-12-28|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417192221/https://lrkm.lrv.lt/en/activities/national-minorities|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據2011的統計資料，全國有85%人口立陶宛語為母語、7.2%以俄語為母語、5.3%以波蘭語為母語，另外全國有39%的人會說俄語、20%會說英語、9%會說[[德語|德語]]、6%會說波蘭語、3%會說[[法語|法語]]<ref name="osp.stat.gov.lt"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://languageknowledge.eu/countries/lithuania|title=Languages in Lithuania|access-date=2018-08-06|archive-date=2018-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323170012/http://languageknowledge.eu/countries/lithuania|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大多數立陶宛學校以英語為第一外語，年輕世代有約80%會說英語<ref>{{Cite web|title=Employees fluent in three languages – it's the norm in Lithuania|url=https://investlithuania.com/news/employees-fluent-in-three-languages-its-the-norm-in-lithuania/|access-date=2021-02-21|website=Invest Lithuania|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624050255/https://investlithuania.com/news/employees-fluent-in-three-languages-its-the-norm-in-lithuania/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[歐洲難民危機|歐洲難民危機]]中，立陶宛依照歐盟成員國的協定接收了一些難民配額<ref>{{cite news |title=Refugees frustrated and trapped in chilly Baltic states |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-40479224 |work=BBC News |date=2017-07-04 |accessdate=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427143715/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-40479224 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年7月，越過[[白俄羅斯-立陶宛邊界|白俄羅斯-立陶宛邊界]]進入立陶宛的非法移民數量大增，導致[[2021年立陶宛移民危機|2021年立陶宛移民危機]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lrytas.lt/pasaulis/ivykiai/2021/07/02/news/ep-pirmininkas-migrantu-antpludis-i-lietuva-kelia-nerima-19955662/|title=EP pirmininkas: migrantų antplūdis į Lietuvą kelia nerimą|publisher=lrytas.lt|date=2021-07-02|access-date=2021-08-01|archive-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712025710/https://www.lrytas.lt/pasaulis/ivykiai/2021/07/02/news/ep-pirmininkas-migrantu-antpludis-i-lietuva-kelia-nerima-19955662/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

