立陶宛的公路運輸也相當發達，2016年與2017年立陶宛的運輸公司均因訂購大批的[[卡車|卡車]]而引起關注<ref>{{cite web|url=http://media.daimler.com/marsMediaSite/en/instance/ko/Largest-Fleet-Order-from-Eastern-Europe-for-Mercedes-Benz-Trucks-in-Its-History-Major-order-of-1000-Mercedes-Benz-Actros-by-Girteka-Logistics.xhtml?oid=9918964|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104150306/http://media.daimler.com/marsMediaSite/en/instance/ko/Largest-Fleet-Order-from-Eastern-Europe-for-Mercedes-Benz-Trucks-in-Its-History-Major-order-of-1000-Mercedes-Benz-Actros-by-Girteka-Logistics.xhtml?oid=9918964|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-04|title=Largest Fleet Order from Eastern Europe for Mercedes-Benz Trucks in Its History: Major order of 1,000 Mercedes-Benz Actros by Girteka Logistics – Daimler Global Media Site|date=2018-01-04|access-date=2021-07-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.volvogroup.com/en-en/news/2017/sep/record-breaking-agreement-for-volvo-trucks.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104150048/http://www.volvogroup.com/en-en/news/2017/sep/record-breaking-agreement-for-volvo-trucks.html|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-04|title=Record breaking agreement for Volvo Trucks – Volvo Group|date=2018-01-04|access-date=2021-07-15}}</ref>，境內約九成的商業卡車運輸為國際運輸，佔比為歐盟中最高<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Freight_transport_statistics|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104135126/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Freight_transport_statistics|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-04|title=Freight transport statistics – Statistics Explained|date=2018-01-04|access-date=2021-07-15}}</ref>。

{{le|克萊佩達港|Port of Klaipėda}}是立陶宛唯一的商港，2011年的貨物交易量為4,550萬公噸（含北側的[[布廷格油庫|布廷格油庫]]）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shortsea.lt/index.php/pagrindinis_meniu/naujienos/klaipedos_ir_kitu_baltijos_juros_rytines_pakrantes_uostu_krovos_apzvalga__m_sausiogruodzio_men_/1201|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019182532/http://www.shortsea.lt/index.php/pagrindinis_meniu/naujienos/klaipedos_ir_kitu_baltijos_juros_rytines_pakrantes_uostu_krovos_apzvalga__m_sausiogruodzio_men_/1201|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2013-10-19|title=SHORT SEA|date=2013-10-19|website=Web.arcive.org|access-date=2018-10-18}}</ref>，此港口是波羅的海地區的第八大港<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baltic-course.com/eng/good_for_business/?doc=90478|title=Riga and Klaipeda included in TOP-10 ports in Baltic Sea Region by container turnover :: The Baltic Course – Baltic States news & analytics|date=2017-12-21|website=Baltic-course.com|access-date=2017-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171221104115/http://www.baltic-course.com/eng/good_for_business/?doc=90478|archive-date=2017-12-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但並未名列歐盟前二十大商港<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Maritime_ports_freight_and_passenger_statistics|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104132949/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Maritime_ports_freight_and_passenger_statistics|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-04|title=Maritime ports freight and passenger statistics – Statistics Explained|date=2018-01-04|access-date=2018-01-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/File:Top_20_container_ports_in_2015_-_on_the_basis_of_volume_of_containers_handled_in_(1000_TEUs).png|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104133109/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/File:Top_20_container_ports_in_2015_-_on_the_basis_of_volume_of_containers_handled_in_(1000_TEUs).png|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-04|title=File:Top 20 container ports in 2015 - on the basis of volume of containers handled in (1000 TEUs).png – Statistics Explained|date=2018-01-04|access-date=2018-01-04}}</ref>，目前有擴建計畫進行中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://port.today/klaipeda-outer-port-constructed/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104132737/https://port.today/klaipeda-outer-port-constructed/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-01-04|title=Klaipeda outer port to be constructed – port.today|date=2018-01-04|access-date=2018-01-04}}</ref>。

[[維爾紐斯國際機場|維爾紐斯國際機場]]為立陶宛最大的機場，2019年在[[全歐洲客運量最多的機場|歐洲機場]]中客運量排名第93，服務旅客約500萬人次<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ltou.lt/uploads/documents/files/apie-oro-uostus/Aviacininkai/Statistika/VNO%202019%20statistics.pdf|title=VNO|website=www.ltou.lt|language=en|access-date=2020-02-06|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120133728/https://www.ltou.lt/uploads/documents/files/apie-oro-uostus/Aviacininkai/Statistika/VNO%202019%20statistics.pdf}}</ref>。其他國際機場還包括[[考纳斯机场|考纳斯机场]]、[[帕蘭加機場|帕蘭加機場]]與[[希奧利艾國際機場|希奧利艾國際機場]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kaunozinios.lt/naujienos/kauno-oro-uoste-ivykdytas-pirmas-reguliarus-krovininis-reisas_36224.html|title=Kauno oro uoste įvykdytas pirmas reguliarus krovininis reisas|website=Kaunozinios.lt|access-date=2021-07-15|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627215332/https://kaunozinios.lt/naujienos/kauno-oro-uoste-ivykdytas-pirmas-reguliarus-krovininis-reisas_36224.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===能源===
