ty and Natural Gas Markets of the Republic of Lithuania to the European Commission|access-date=2018-03-19|archive-date=2021-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623222139/https://www.ceer.eu/documents/104400/3736793/C16_NR_Lithuania-EN.pdf/1c379f34-4e09-7311-e715-5974e45eab3f|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此外還有波蘭與立陶宛間的{{tsl|en|Gas Interconnection Poland–Lithuania|波蘭-立陶宛油氣管道|油氣管道}}正在興建中<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ambergrid.lt/lt/projektai/dujotiekiu-jungtis-tarp-lenkijos-ir-lietuvos-gipl|title=Dujotiekių jungtis tarp Lenkijos ir Lietuvos (GIPL)|access-date=2021-07-15|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128221106/https://www.ambergrid.lt/lt/projektai/dujotiekiu-jungtis-tarp-lenkijos-ir-lietuvos-gipl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

